Making bonder
Step one: install boost 
sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev
If you do not have administrative access, install boost locally and edit the makefile 
Step two: run make
step 3 copy the bond excutable to where you want to install it

Usage
bond h will give the varous modes the program has
calling bond with just a letter will tell you the proper arguments for that mode of opperation
bonder is more useful with bonder tools, these tools will automaticly run bonder with specific arguments the corispond to commen usages

